Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.28,0:22:32.62,ED64 Roma,,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(450,450)}Masshiro na keshiki ni ima sasowarete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:39.17,ED64 Eng,,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(450,450)}I'm headed toward an unseen world.
