Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:48.09,ED64 Roma,,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(450,0)}Maigo no mama tabi shiteita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.09,0:22:50.89,ED64 Eng,,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(450,0)}Under this gray sky.
